                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.51/48.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">American Chargé d’Affaires</gloss> to
                        the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegrams.—Extracts.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Mexico</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1912-11-12T17:00:00-06:36">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 12, 1912—5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Finances of Mexico in hopeless confusion and bankruptcy seems rapidly
                    approaching.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Schuyler.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
